* [Gamification Community](http://www.gamificationcommunity.com) -  A community of people interested in gamification, sharing use-cases, ideas, and looking for projects and experts
* [SAP Gamification](http://scn.sap.com/community/gamification) - A community of people interested in gamification around SAP
* [Masters of Gamification](http://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=3674916) - LinkedIn group centered around gamification
* [EDUCAUSE Games and Learning](https://m.facebook.com/groups/164657036902579) - Facebook group centered around games in education
* [Game Changer - Gamification to Engage Employees](http://www.engagingleader.com/group/) - LinkedIn group for people interested in internal gamification
* [LinkedIn Gamification Groups](http://www.linkedin.com/search-fe/group_search?pplSearchOrigin=GLHD&keywords=gamification) - A dynamic link to all LinkedIn groups related to gamification
